casebody.data:
Ninti EL BEY
v.
COUNTY OF MECKLENBURG, Register of Deeds David Granberry, Official and Individual Capacity No. 300P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 22, 2016 Ms. Ninti El-Bey, Pro se. Mr. Robert S. Adden, Jr., Attorney at Law, For Mecklenburg County, et al.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Petitioner on the 16th of August 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Mecklenburg County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 22nd of September 2016."
